properties.areaDesc: Waters from Point Pinos to Point Piedras Blancas 10-60 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 5 at 8:47AM PST until January 6 at 9:00AM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 20 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and seas
8 to 10 feet at 13 seconds expected.

* WHERE...Waters from Point Pinos to Point Piedras Blancas 10-
60 NM.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM PST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM PST MONDAY... ...GALE WARNING WILL EXPIRE AT 9 AM PST THIS MORNING
